(text "NOTES:" (at 20.32 229.87 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid c57c25d7-5f33-5cfe-b9c3-dd3fa535c297))
(text "J310 is deliberately pin-reversed relative to J320 for two top-side FH12 bottom-contact connectors and a Type-A same-side FFC." (at 20.32 237.49 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 9f240ea4-140e-51d0-bc99-2fc0f6dd048e))
(text "Specified cable: Molex 0150200315, 30 circuits, 0.5 mm pitch, 30 mm, Type A / same-side contacts." (at 20.32 245.11 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 56d38ac1-409c-5be6-9651-021d0d4f166b))
(text "R386/R387 stay DNP. U310 limits the future RGB rail below 0.5A/contact and defaults off; rev A has no RGB load." (at 20.32 252.73 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid d6d9c3e5-2a57-548f-b34e-bc2836b4f982))
(text "J310 pin 3 / rev-A J320 pin 28 repurposes unused COL15 for RGB data. Rows 5..7 and COL14 remain spare." (at 20.32 260.35 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 06c7615c-aba1-5aec-b746-375a4fa3c829))
(text "Rev B must add local LED bulk capacitance and firmware must enforce a 325mA LED budget; unrestricted full-white is unsupported." (at 20.32 267.97 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 24b5c535-7145-59f5-af20-21f13f54e7ed))
